parameters:
...I can't use teleportation and I need to go
through the reception for procedures...!

Well then, let's get right to healing. But... I'll
need your power as well.
I understand my power now! So, what should I do?

Yes, I will now send your consciousness... your
heart, into the heart of my child.

And most likely, there should be gloomy figures in
the depths of your heart. The purpose this time is
to release those figures.

...You casually mentioned something amazing, like
sending hearts...

Well then, it's quite an amazing thing. There's no
one else but me who can use such advanced magic.

Well then, even though I'm quite skilled, I have
to concentrate intensely while using this
technique.

During that time, I won't be able to observe
what's happening inside. In other words, you alone
will have to release the gloom.

...The inside of your heart is an unstable place.
There is a fear that it may have some physical
effects. Still... will you do it?
Of course. My determination hasn't changed.

Hehehe... As expected of the woman I had in
mind... Well then, now that we're prepared, let's
get started...

Um... just one thing... how can I release the
gloom inside my heart?

Hehehe... That will be useful, the experiences you
have had. And gloom takes on a human form... Do
you understand?
Alright, now that you understand... Let's go!
Shu... ja... gyuu... ko... you...    Haa!!

The method is the same as last time. I will send
you into my son's heart and release your lust.

The difference from last time is going deeper into
the depths of the heart and having a stronger
lustful aura, these two things.

The level of danger has increased, are you still
going?

That was a foolish question. Well then...
\.\{Ha!!}
Are you awake... How are you feeling?
Yes... I'm still feeling a bit dazed...

It seems you were affected by the lewd aura. Even
if you have some resistance, there are limits.

Furthermore, your soul has been burdened by the
spell. Rest well tonight, and we will talk once
morning comes...
Haru-kun... I'm glad... I'm really glad...

Haruto: Good morning... Mom... \.\. ...Huh...? Are
you crying...?

Mmm... I just yawned and tears came out, that's
all...

Haruto: I see... yawn... I'm still sleepy too, so
just a little longer...

Alright...! Just a little more! This time, I'll
erase all of the lewd energy!

But, I can't immediately let you into my heart,
Rei-san. Today, for now, I'll go home...

Oh, oh...? Did you already go home...?\!... I'm
tired too, so let's go home and rest quickly.

Alright, are you ready? Let's tighten our focus so
we can give it our all until the end.

And thanks to regaining my powers, I can now
understand your condition better than before.
If there's anything, I'll also give you advice.

Haru: Good morning, Mom! Geez, you were sleeping
again!
Hehe... Sorry, I was a little tired.

Haru: ...Huh? It feels like it's been a while
since I've seen Mom...?

That's right, Haru-kun, you've been taking
afternoon naps for a while. Hmm... I wonder how
many days you've been sleeping...

Haru: Well then... since it's been a while, I'll
give you a tight hug!
Really? Then maybe I should ask for a favor♪
Haru: A-Are you okay? Did it hurt?
Haru: I see... Hey, Mom? When can I go home?

I'm sure you'll be able to go home soon. When you
do, let's have a feast together, okay?

Oh, I have a lot of printouts from school, so I
have to do those too.

(Haru-kun's smile... It always gives me strength.
It's the greatest happiness as a mother.)

(But... through this strange experience, I've come
to realize...)

(I... as much as being a mother... also identify
as a \c[27]woman\c[0].)

(As much as the happiness of being a mother... I
will also find happiness as a woman...♡)
